header

Class ESA

  • java.lang.Object
    • header.ESA
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ESAChannel, ESATemplateChannel

    public class ESA
extends java.lang.Object
    ESA is to record attributes of a single channel contained in an EDF file. ESAHeader, in comparison, records attributes of all channels, one by one, contained in an EDF file
